{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeTagComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for tag component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the tag component tokens you want.","","        override var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken  { borders.radiusNone }","","        override var sizeMinWidthMedium: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._500 }","","        override var spacePaddingInlineIconStartSmall: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineMedium }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: TagComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"typ